# results

**Interface Property**

An array of places that returns from a geocoder lookup or reverse lookup.

## Declaration

```swift
results: Place[];
```

## Discussion

An object the system parses from the geocoder JSON response, which contains an array of places. Each [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/Place] has several properties.

If there’s no response, [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/GeocoderResponse/results] is an empty array.
